description:
&lt;p&gt;Recruitment Virtual Open Day –24th November 2020 @ 3pm for our Kensington &amp; Chelsea &amp; North Westminster adult community services – CLCH NHS Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CLCH’s Kensington &amp; Chelsea &amp; North Westminster adult community nursing team are holding an interactive virtual open day with the opportunity for you to ask us questions in relation to our vacancies, secure an interview on the day; meet our Team plus opportunity for us to provide you with realistic hands on information about who we are and our passion for providing great healthcare closer to home&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have vacancies in the following areas&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Community Nurse –x3 band 5 – North Kensington and Chelsea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Community Nurse –x5 band 5 – North West Westminster&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Community Nurse –x1 band 5 – South Kensington and Chelsea&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We invite you to join our dynamic team. Where you will have the ability to work in a multi-disciplinary environment, so an individualised approach to care can be achieved whilst making a real impact on promoting health and well-being.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In addition, we will also provide you with: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent progression through various career pathway opportunities through our Academy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and guidance with Revalidation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ongoing supervision and appraisals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent staff benefits: which includes- childcare vouchers, health and wellbeing services, season ticket loans, cycle to work scheme plus many more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;to If you are interested in attending our Virtual Recruitment Day, please send an email to Jackie.cloake@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Should you wish to speak with someone about the various vacancies we have indicated in this advert please contact Eleanor Levi Business support via email Eleanor.levi@nhs.net who will put you in touch with one of the District Nurse Team Leads&lt;/p&gt;
